&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Trust has a no smoking policy and all premises are considered as non smoking zones. In addition, smoking is not allowed in staff cars that are parked on trust property and during the working day, smoking is prohibited whilst in uniform wherever an employee is located.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
